  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Fuuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Used mainly by scouts and messengers, this technique allows you to send a spoken message of no more than twenty five words or sounds, spoken by anyone within 15 ft as it is performed, or the wind can simply send a faint sensation of stirring air. The message is carried upon the winds, traveling anywhere between 20 ft per round to 1 ft per minute, and the spoken message or sensation is delivered if it reaches its destination before the duration ends. If you lose consciousness, have your Chakra Pool reduced to 0 or die before the wind reaches its destination, the message is lost.</p>\n\n\n\n",
